data.description: Nestled within the sought after Tortosa community, this remarkable residence redefines the very essence of beauty. 7 generous bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms! As you arrive you are greeted by a three-stall garage for your cars, toys and storage needs. The heart of this home is an open-concept kitchen, complete with a magnificent island, a chef's dream come true. Outfitted with gas cooking, craft delectable feasts for your loved ones, and relish the convenience and sophistication that this space affords. The living areas within this residence are grand in scale, offering an abundance of room for entertaining and relaxation. The inclusion of a sprawling loft enhances the overall sense of spaciousness and offers endless possibilities, from a home theater to a private study The master suite is ginormous, where you can escape the demands of the world. The en-suite bathroom provides an oversized tub, a separate shower, and dual vanities. Step outside, and you'll discover a backyard that offers a tranquil retreat, complete with an extended covered patio. This private sanctuary is ideal for enjoying the Arizona sunshine in style.
